For gedit:
if your system is using gtksourceview-1.0 (CADE lab), put cs3710-1.0.lang into 
~/.gnome2/gtksourceview-1.0/language-specs/
if your system is using gtksourceview-2.0, put cs3710-2.0.lang into
~/.local/share/gtksourceview-2.0/language-specs/

For Notepad++:
View>User-Defined Dialogue...
Click "Import", then select cs3710-npp.xml